---
<Layout title="How Undocumented Individuals Can Obtain an ITIN and Pay Taxes" lang="es" langHref="/en/itin-undocumented">
<section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Inicio</a> <span>›</span> <a href="/blog">Blog</a> <span>›</span> <span>ITIN</span></div><h1>How Undocumented Individuals Can Obtain an ITIN and Pay Taxes</h1><p></p></div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="post-layout">
<article>
  <div class="post-meta"><span>2024</span><span class="blog-tag">ITIN</span><span>Guzman Tax Accounting</span></div>
  <div class="post-featured-img"><img src="/assets/vendedor-de-aguas-frescas.png" alt="How Undocumented Individuals Can Obtain an ITIN and Pay Taxes" loading="lazy"/></div>
  <div class="post-content"><p>Many undocumented individuals living and working in the United States believe they cannot or should not file taxes. This is a common misconception. The IRS allows anyone with income in the U.S. to file taxes, regardless of immigration status, using an <strong>Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN)</strong>.</p><h2>What is an ITIN?</h2><p>An ITIN is a tax processing number issued by the IRS for individuals who do not have a Social Security Number (SSN). It is used exclusively for tax purposes and does not authorize work or provide eligibility for Social Security benefits.</p><h2>How to Apply for an ITIN</h2><ul><li>Complete <strong>Form W-7</strong> (IRS Application for ITIN)</li><li>Provide proof of identity (passport, national ID, etc.)</li><li>Submit your tax return with your W-7</li><li>Work with a Certifying Acceptance Agent (CAA) like us</li></ul><h2>Benefits of Filing Taxes with an ITIN</h2><ul><li>Builds a tax history, which may help immigration processes</li><li>Allows access to certain tax credits</li><li>Demonstrates compliance with U.S. tax law</li></ul><a href="/consulta-gratuita" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:8px;">Consulta Confidencial Gratis</a></div>
  <div style="margin-top:40px;padding:28px;background:var(--gray);border-radius:12px;text-align:center;">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom:10px;">¿Necesitas Ayuda con tus Taxes?</h3>
    <p style="color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:20px;">Agenda una consulta gratuita con nuestros expertos. Atención en español.</p>
    <a href="/consulta-gratuita" class="btn btn-primary">Consulta Gratuita</a>
  </div>
</article>
<BlogSidebar lang="es" />
</div></div></section>
</Layout>
